{"tid":2130672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"智利傳選用日本太平洋光纜線路，放棄將上海作為最終目的地","createTime":"2020-07-29T10:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T10:56:12.000Z","uid":75656,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c21645a5046765041c3589a0e2ed949967376dfc","tid":2130672,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"美國積極動員各國將中國排除在全球電訊項目之外的時候，日媒引述知情人士報道，智利選擇了日本提議的一條太平洋光纜線路，作為首條將南美與亞太地區直接相連的光纜線路。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，中國曾游說將上海納入有關光纜計劃，華為並承諾會投資智利的數據中心，而中國的原本希望是將上海作為路線的最終目的地，但現時的光纜路線的終點將為澳洲和紐西蘭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=599718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fid%3D599718&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6U2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=e232d63f\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=599718</a>"},{"pid":"74bd3cf73c4389889c74c55a4d5034a879fa58ef","tid":2130672,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59f4063e780ee555dcfaafdc5f19316d3be86e3","tid":2130672,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:53:52.000Z","msg":"香港變台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上海變日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球脫支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0634aa408fef2a7bf97d9581d62f0a75246c1e1","tid":2130672,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:54:55.000Z","msg":"中國=全球最大規模內聯網"},{"pid":"53e46460350f6e77b5e11da5ac27521764d2d6be","tid":2130672,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"美國咁個制可以關閉中國互聯網"},{"pid":"f7f8e34fb6ec7cae